<p><a href="http://tbone.biol.sc.edu/tide/tideshow.cgi?site=Alcatraz+Island+S%2C+San+Francisco+Bay%2C+California+Current">Tide &#038; Current Alcatraz South</a></p>
<p><a href="http://tidesandcurrents.noaa.gov/data_menu.shtml?stn=9414290%20San%20Francisco,%20CA&#038;type=Meteorological+Observations">Tides, Wind, H2O &#038; Water Temp 1</a></p>
